name: FLContactIdentifiersCreateTable
rule:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `Contact Identifiers` (
  `type` varbinary(64) NOT NULL,
  `value` varbinary(256) NOT NULL,
  `Contact ID` bigint(20) unsigned NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`type`,`value`,`Contact ID`),
  KEY `type` (`type`),
  KEY `value` (`value`),
  KEY `Contact ID` (`Contact ID`) USING BTREE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci
